easy to make and really nice on a rainy day. i added more wine than requested and received rave reviews from my dinner guest.

Rating: 2
This was pretty good considering it is very healthy. I followed the recipe exactly. Next time I would cut down on the wine to 1/2 cup. I chopped up the chicken before serving to make it easier to eat and served it with some whole grain french bread.